sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor       User as User
    participant FE    as Frontend<br/>(Next.js)
    participant BE    as Backend<br/>(NestJS)
    participant DB    as Database

    %% ── Phase 1: Post Reactions (Like & Save) ──────────────────────
    rect rgb(239, 246, 255)
        Note over User,DB: Phase 1 — Post Reactions (Like & Save)

        User ->>+ FE : Click Like / Save icon on Post
        FE ->>+ BE : POST /api/posts/:id/like (or /save)
        Note over BE : JwtAuthGuard + BannedUserGuard + EmailVerifiedGuard

        BE ->>+ DB : Toggle Like/SavedPost record & count active likes
        DB -->>- BE : Toggle status & new like count
        BE -) BE : notificationsService.emit('LIKE') (if liked)

        BE -->>- FE : 200 OK — { liked/saved: boolean, count?: number }
        FE -->>- User : Render updated state & count (revert if error)
    end

    %% ── Phase 2: Post Reposting (Simple & Quote Repost) ───────────
    rect rgb(240, 253, 244)
        Note over User,DB: Phase 2 — Post Reposting

        User ->>+ FE : Click Repost or enter quote description & click "Quote"
        FE ->>+ BE : POST /api/posts/:id/repost { desc? }
        Note over BE : JwtAuthGuard + BannedUserGuard + EmailVerifiedGuard

        BE ->>+ DB : Create repost / toggle soft-delete & count reposts
        DB -->>- BE : Repost record & active repost count
        BE -) BE : notificationsService.emit('REPOST') (if created)

        BE -->>- FE : 200 OK — { reposted: boolean, count: number }
        FE ->> FE : Invalidate query cache ["posts"]
        FE -->>- User : Update repost status & count in UI
    end

    %% ── Phase 3: Commenting & Replying ─────────────────────────────
    rect rgb(254, 243, 199)
        Note over User,DB: Phase 3 — Commenting & Replying

        User ->>+ FE : Type comment/reply, attach files, click Comment/Reply
        FE ->>+ BE : POST /api/posts/:postId/comments (multipart/form-data)
        Note over BE : JwtAuthGuard + EmailVerifiedGuard
        BE ->> BE : Save files to Cloudinary (if any)

        BE ->>+ DB : Create Comment with media, parentCommentId?, & parsed mentions
        DB -->>- BE : Created Comment record
        BE -) BE : notificationsService.emit('REPLY' / 'MENTION')

        BE -->>- FE : 201 Created — Comment JSON
        FE ->> FE : Invalidate query cache ["comments", postId]
        FE -->>- User : Append comment to thread & update comments count
    end

    %% ── Phase 4: Comment Management (Edit, Delete, Like) ──────────
    rect rgb(250, 250, 250)
        Note over User,DB: Phase 4 — Comment Management

        User ->>+ FE : Edit body/media, click Delete, or click Comment Like
        FE ->>+ BE : PATCH /api/comments/:id | DELETE /api/comments/:id | POST /api/comments/:id/like
        Note over BE : Guards check jwt, banned state, email verification

        BE ->>+ DB : Update comment / soft-delete / toggle CommentLike & count
        DB -->>- BE : Updated comment record / toggle status & count
        BE -) BE : notificationsService.emit('LIKE') (if comment liked)

        BE -->>- FE : 200 OK — Success response
        FE ->> FE : Invalidate query cache ["comments", postId]
        FE -->>- User : Update comment body, remove from list, or toggle like status
    end
